entries.s_246: Nothing right now. I'm looking for someone.
entries.s_249: And I expect you think I know where this someone is?

entries.s_254: Sure. Good customer, a bit too good if you know what I mean. Last time he was in here, he said he was heading to Nashal, on the planet Talus.
